     "order": 1,
     "attributes": {
      "subject": "Small habits, big difference — {{contact.first_name}}",
      "html": "<p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">Hi {{contact.first_name}},<br></p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">It's been about a month since we saw you at Men's Wellness Centers, and</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">we wanted to check in — no agenda, just a few things worth passing along.</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">Most men tell us the changes that made the biggest difference weren't</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">dramatic. They were small and repeatable:<br></p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">- Getting to bed and waking up at consistent times, even on weekends</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">- Ten minutes of morning light before the phone comes out</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">- Protein earlier in the day instead of loading it all at dinner</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">- A short daily walk — not a workout, just movement<br></p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">None of this is a substitute for what we talked about in your consult —</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">it's just the groundwork that makes everything else work better.</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">And whenever you're ready to pick up where we left off, your consult</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">notes are still on file. Restarting is a short conversation, not a</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">do-over.<br></p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">Take care of yourself,</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">The Men's Wellness Centers Team – Richmond</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">(757) 806-6263</p>",
      "from_name": "",
      "from_email": "",
