    {
     "id": "4055a5f6-00b9-4dd5-8173-66e3b870383b",
     "parent": "dbbaf477-fc97-454d-9bd7-fc64fc33f091",
     "order": 5,
     "attributes": {
      "subject": "The season most men let it slide — {{contact.first_name}}",
      "html": "<p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">Hi {{contact.first_name}},<br></p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">There's a stretch every year shorter days, colder mornings, the</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">schedule gets heavier where energy and motivation tend to dip for a</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">lot of men.<br><br>It's common enough that it's almost predictable.</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">If you've noticed it in yourself lately, you're not imagining it, and</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">you're not alone in it. It's also the time of year where the men who</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">stay consistent sleep, movement, the basics notice the biggest gap</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">between how they feel and how everyone around them feels.</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">We're still here, and your consult is still on file. If the timing feels</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">better now than it did a few months ago, picking it back up takes about</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">ten minutes.<br></p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">No pressure either way just didn't want the season to pass without</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">checking in.<br></p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">The Men's Wellness Centers Team – Richmond</p><p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">(757) 806-6263</p>",
